title: Police to be out in force for long weekend
text:
Police to be out in force for long we... Police to be out in force for long weekend Next Story Prev Story 2 hrs ago Read more: Star 
Long weekenders will wake on Friday morning knowing the doubling of demerit points had kicked in until Monday night, as holidaymakers take advantage of the warming spring weather and families begin returning home for the return of school. Senior police have also warned footy fans to behave during grand final celebrations and remain on alert if they are travelling to the games.   Star.
